title: [1508521049] Gordon Ramsay | How to Extract ALL the Meat from a Lobster
description:
On the new ITV show Culinary Genius, Gordon sets the amateur chefs the tricky task of extracting ALL the meat from a lobster. Before they start, Chef Ramsay himself gives a masterclass demonstration.
Subscribe for weekly cooking videos.
